wiki.summary: “ExtraL” is the third single from JENNIE’s debut solo studio album, Ruby, featuring Grammy-winning Tampa rapper Doechii. This empowering hip-hop anthem encourages women to embrace their inner strengths and confidence. The official music video for the song directed by Cole Bennett of Lyrical Lemonade continues to explore the artistic and supernatural themes introduced in JENNIE’s previous singles, as well as the visualizer for the ninth track on Ruby titled “ZEN,” the idea of which was crafted by Cho Giseok. Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: “ExtraL” is the third single from JENNIE’s debut solo studio album, Ruby, featuring Grammy-winning Tampa rapper Doechii. This empowering hip-hop anthem encourages women to embrace their inner strengths and confidence. The official music video for the song directed by Cole Bennett of Lyrical Lemonade continues to explore the artistic and supernatural themes introduced in JENNIE’s previous singles, as well as the visualizer for the ninth track on Ruby titled “ZEN,” the idea of which was crafted by Cho Giseok. Doechii: “She’s a star. She’s really inspiring. I like how professional and involved she is. We’re both involved in that same way, and I respect and like that about her.
